.com/news/heres-what-tulsi-gabbard-plans-to-reveal-before-leaving-office", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Weekly Gabbard Declassification Drops for the Next Month? Covid? Havana Syndrome? I\u2019m here for this. Big league. ", "last_comment_created": 1779726380625, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 32, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "WASHINGTON\u2014 Director of National Intelligence Tulsi Gabbard plans to release findings from a number of high-profile investigations before she departs her role as President Donald Trump\u2019s spy chief, The Daily Wire has learned.Gabbard announced Friday that she will resign, sharing that her husband is battling \u201can extremely rare form of bone cancer\u201d and that she must \u201cstep away from public service to be by his side and fully support him through this battle.\u201d She will remain in her position until June 30, an intelligence official confirmed to The Daily Wire.Before departing, Gabbard intends to release findings tied to investigations into Havana Syndrome, formally known as Anomalous Health Incidents (AHIs), the COVID-19 pandemic, the weaponization of the federal government, the 2020 presidential election, and more, according to the official. These findings will likely be released in weekly installments over the next month.Principal Deputy Director of National Intelligence Aaron Lukas will serve as Acting Director", "large_image": "jlpWxcbkdPHZBEnV.png", "title": "Here\u2019s What Tulsi Gabbard Plans To Reveal Before Leaving Office"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2058761313749532916", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid"